Yes, you can buff and heal most pets in the game.  I don't play with pet clases too oftem, but they can be very handy.  I have to agree with most here, pets are generally expendable, other than in specific situations.  <P>Also, I rarily keep track of the pet's health, I'm usually too busy keeping track of my group's health.  If a request is made for a pet heal, I'll guage the situation and if mana permits, I'll usually cast a greater heal (usually enough to keep it alive, but thier regen rate is pretty amazing, so don't usually "top off").  If I'm low, I let the mag/necro know that I'm not in a position to do do a heal.<P>~Fuzzy~<P>--------------------<P>Confuzzed NoMoure<BR>53 Cleric<BR>Cleric Leader: Legion of Velious<BR>Quellious Server
